    "SimplifiedChinese": "合金金属",
    "TencentChinese": "合金金属",
    "TraditionalChinese": "合金"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A lightweight and highly malleable alloy. Crafted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Paraffinium</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ionized Cobalt</span>.<br><br>In high demand on the Galactic Trade Network due to its utility in the construction of planetside outposts and facilities.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "可塑性很强的轻质合金。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">矿脂</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">离子钴</span>制作而成。<br><br>此金属广泛运用于行星前哨基站与设施的建筑工作，在银河交易网络中十分抢手。",
    "TencentChinese": "可塑性很强的轻质合金。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">石蜡</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">氯</span>制作而成。<br><br>此金属广泛运用于行星前哨基站与设施的建筑工作，在银河交易网络中十分抢手。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "輕量、延展性高的合金。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">鑞</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">離子化鈷</span>製作而成。<br><br>因為建築行星基地與設施時會大量使用，所以銀河交易網對此材料有極高需求。"
  },
